hadiths[90]{hadithnumber,text}:
3326,"Hazrat Qais bin Abi Gharzaa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein ham tajiron ko (سماسرہ) (dalaal) kaha jata tha, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas se guzrey aur hamein is se behtar naam diya aur farmaya : ''aey tajiron ki jamaat ! kharid aur farokht aur lain dain mein bahut si be-jaa baaten hoti hain aur qasmen bhi khai jati hain, to is mein sadqa mila liya karo.''"
3327,Hazrat Qais bin Abi Gharzaa (Raziallahu anhu) ne mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya aur kaha : ''lain-dain aur tijaarati umur (baton) tey kartey huey jhoot aur qasam shamil ho jati hai.'' Abdullah Zohri ne  ''laghw (fuzul aur bekar) aur jhoot'' ke alfaz riwayat kiye hain.
3328,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs apney maqrooz ke sath chimat gaya jisney uskey das Dinar deney they. usney kaha : Allah ki qasam ! jab tak to mujhey dey nahin deta mein tujhey hergiz nahin chhodun ga , siwaye iskey ke to koi zaamin ya kafeel ley aaye . to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wo apney zimmey ley liye . phir wo aadmi hasabe-wada (wade ke waqt par) maal lekar aaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se daryaft farmaya : ''tumhen ye sona kahan se mil gaya hai?'' usney kaha : eik kaan se. aapney farmaya : ''hamen iski zarurat nahin (aur) is mein khair nahin.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski taraf se qarz ada farma diya."
3329,"Janab Sha'bi (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu Anhuma) se suna aur unke baad kisi aur se sunney ki mujhey koi hajat nahin (kyonkey wo eik sachchay sahabi they) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''bila-shuba halal wazeh hai aur haram bhi wazeh hai aur unke beech kaee umur (baton) shubhe waley hain. main tumhen iski baabat misal bayan karta hun. Allah taala ki eik charaagaah hai (mehfooz makhsus ilaaqa jisey rakh ya mahfooza kaha jata hai) aur Allah ki rakh aur uska mahfooza wohi hai jo usney haram kiya hai, jo shakhs us mehfooz ilaqey ke qarib apney janwer charaaey ga qarib hai ke wo us mein ja padey. aur jo shak wali baaton mein padta hai qarib hai ke wo un mein (be-dhadak) jur'at kerney lagey.''"
3330,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap ye hadees bayan farmatey they. aapney farmaya : ''aur in (halal aur haram) ke darmiyan kuchh shubhe wali chizen hain jinhen aksar log nahin jantey , to jo shub'haat se bach gaya usney apni izzat aur apney deen ko mehfooz kar liya aur jo shubhe wali chizon mein ja pada wo haram mein dakhil hua ''"
3331,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yaqeenan eik waqt aaney wala hai ke logon mein se koi bhi na bachey ga jo sood na khata ho, isliye agar kisi ne na bhi khaya tab bhi uski bhaap to usey pahunchey gi.''  ibne Esa ne ye alfaz zikr kiye hain : ''uska kuchh ghubar usey pahunchey ga.''"
3332,"Janab Aasim bin Kulaib apney walid se wo eik Ansari jawan se riwayat kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eik janaazey mein gaey. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko qabr par dekha, aap qabr khodney waley ko hidayaat dey rahey they : ''paainti ki taraf se khuli karo, sar ki taraf se khuli karo.'' jab aap wapis huey to aap ko eik aurat ki taraf se dawat deney wala mila . to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey yahaan tashrif ley aaye , khana pesh kiya gaya to aapney apna haath badhaya phir logon ne bhi apney haath badhaey aur khaney lagey . hamarey badon ne dekha ke aap eik hi luqma apney munh mein ghumaaey ja rahey hain (magar nigalte nahin) aapney farmaya : ''main mehsoos karta hun ke ye gosht aisi bakri ka hai jisey uskey Malik ki ijazat ke baghair liya gaya hai.'' phir (us aurat ko bulwaya gaya to) usney paigham bhijwaayaa : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine Baqee ki taraf aadmi bheja ke merey liye bakri kharid laye magar nahin mili . phir maine apney hamsaaey ki taraf bheja jisney eik bakri khareedi thi , maine kahlwaayaa ke usi qeemat par bakri mujhey dey dey magar wo bhi nahin mila . tab maine us aadmi ki biwi ko kehla bheja to usney mujhey ye bhej di. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye khana qaidiyon ko khila dey.''"
3333,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sood khaney , khilaney , uskey gawah aur likhney waley (sab) par lanat farmaee hai."
3334,"Janab Sulaiman bin Amr apney walid (Amr bin Ahwas Jushmi (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke maine Hajjatul-wadaa mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' khabrdar ! jahiliyat ke tamam sood batil kiye jatey hain, tumharey liye tumhara asal maal hai, zulm karo na zulm kiye jao, khabrdar ! jahiliyat ke tamam khoon batil kiye jatey hain, aur sab se pehla khoon jo main khatam kar raha hun Haris bin Abdul-Muttalib ka khoon hai, jo bano Leis mein doodh peeta bachcha tha aur bano Huzail ne usey qatl kar diya tha.'' raawi ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! maine pahuncha diya.'' sab haazirin ne kaha : haan . aapney teen baar kahlwaayaa . phir aapney farmaya : ''aey Allah ! gawah rehna.'' teen baar kaha."
3335,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : ''qasam se sauda bik jata hai magar barkat uth jati hai. ibne Sarah ne (سلعة) ki bajaey (كسب) kaha. aur sanad mein yun kaha : (عن  سعيد بن المسيب  ،  عن  أبي هريرة  ، an النبي ﷺ) ."
3336,"Hazrat Suwaid bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke main aur Mukhrifa Abdi (Raziallahu anhu) bahreen ke ilaaqe hijr se kapda laye aur ham usey Makka ley aaye , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chaltey huey hamarey paas tashrif laye, aapney ham se eik paajame ka sauda kiya jo ham ne aap ko bechaa aur wahan eik aadmi tha jo mazduri lekar maal tolta tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : ''taulo aur jhuktaa hua taulo.''"
3337,Hazrat Abu-Safwaan bin Umaira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke hijrat kerney se pehley main makkey mein aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua . aur ye mazkura baala hadees bayan ki . magar is mein ''mazduri par maal tolney '' ka bayan nahin hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : isko Qais ne (bhi) isi tarah bayan kiya hai jaisey ke Sufiyan ne aur Sufiyan ka qaul ziyada behtar hai.
3338,"Ibne-Abi Rizma kehtey hain ke maine apney walid se suna ke eik shakhs ne Shoba se kaha ke Sufiyan ne aap ki mukhalifat ki hai. to unhoney kaha : to ne mujhey bahut pareshan kiya hai. halanke mujhey Yahya bin Moayan ki ye baat pahunchi hai ke jo bhi Sufiyan ki mukhalifat karey, to baat Sufiyan ki ziyada behtar hogi ."
3339,Shoba (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke Sufiyan mujh se ziyada haafiz they.
3340,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wazan ehle-Makka ka moatabar hai aur mikyaal (naapney ka paimana) ehale-Madina ka . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Faryabi aur Abu-Ahmad ne bhi Sufiyan se aisey hi riwayat kiya hai, ibne Dakeen ne in dono ki matan (asl ibarat) mein muwaafiqat ki hai (na ke sanad mein) Abu-Ahmad ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki bajaey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka naam liya hai. Waleed bin Muslim ne Hanzala se riwayat ki to kaha : wazan ehale-Madina ka moatabar hai aur mikyaal ehle-Makka ka. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : Malik bin Dinar ki is baarey mein hadees jo ba-waaste Ata Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marwi (bayan) hai, iskey matan mein ikhtilaf kiya gaya hai."
3341,Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein khutba diya aur puchha : ''kya bani falan mein se koi yahan hai? '' magar kisi ne jawab na diya. aapney dobara puchha : ''kya bani falan mein se koi yahan hai? '' lekin kisi ne jawab na diya. aapney teesri baar puchha : ''kya bani falan mein se koi yahan hai? '' to eik aadmi khada hua aur usney kaha : main hun aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney farmaya : ''tujhey kya maane (rukawat) hua tha ke pehli aur dusri baar jawab nahin diya tha? bila-shuba maine tumharey liye khair hi ka irada kiya hai. tumhara sathi apney qarzey mein pakda hua hai.'' (Samura (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke) phir maine us shakhs ko dekha ke usney us (maqrooz) ki taraf se sab ada kar diya yahan tak ke koi mutalba kerney wala baqi na raha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke (Sha'bi ke Shaikh ka naam) Sam'aan bin Mushnaj hai.
3342,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke nazdik uskey mana karda bade gunah ke baad sab se bada gunah ye hai ke bandey par jab maut aaye to wo maqrooz ho aur usney adaegi ke liye kuchh na chhoda ho.''"
3343,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi aisey aadmi ka janaza na padhaya kartey they jis par qarza baqi hota, eik maiyat ko laya gaya to aapney puchha : ''kya is par qarza hai? '' Sahaba ne kaha : haan do Dinar hai. aapney farmaya : ''tum log apney sathi ka janaza padh lo.'' phir Hazrat Abu-Qatada Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wo merey zimmey hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska janaza padhaya . phir jab Allah ne apney Rasool ke liye futoohaat ka darwaza khol diya to aapney farmaya : ''main her momin ke liye uski jaan se qarib tar hun. so jisney koi qarza chhoda uski adaegi merey zimmey hai aur jisney koi maal chhoda ho to wo uskey warison ka hai.''"
3344,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is hadees ki jaisi riwayat ki aur kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik qafiley walon se koi chiz khareedi. us waqt aap ke paas qeemat na thi , phir aap ko us par munaafa diya gaya to aapney farokht kar di , phir aapney uska munaafa banu-Abdul Muttalib ki bewaaon par sadqa kar diya aur farmaya : ''aainda main koi cheez tabhi khareedoonga jab merey paas uski qeemat hogi.''"
3345,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghani (maaldar) aadmi ka qarzey ki adaegi ko taaley jana zulm hai, aur jab tum mein se kisi ko kisi ghani ke hawaley kiya jaey to usey chahiye ke wo is baat ko maan ley.''"
3346,"Hazrat Abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (eik baar) eik jawan oont udhaar liya , phir aap ke paas sadqey ke oont aagey . aapney mujh se farmaya ke uska ( jawan ( oont ada kar don . maine arz kiya : galley mein uskey oont se umda rubaai oont hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey wohi dey do , logon mein behtareen wohi hotey hain jo adaegi mein behtareen hon.''"
3347,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par mera kuchh qarza tha, aapney mujhey wo ada farmaya to us se ziyada diya."
3348,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''soney ke badley chaandi sood hai siwaye iskey ke haathon haath (naqad) ho, gehun ke badley gehun sood hai siwaye iskey ke haathon haath ho, khajoor ke badley khajoor sood hai siwaye iskey ke haathon haath ho. jau ke badley jau sood hai siwaye iskey ke haathon haath ho.''"
3349,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''soney ke badley sona dalaa ho ya dhalaa hua (sikka ya zewar), chaandi ke badley chaandi dalaa ho ya dhalaa hua (sikka ya zewar) , gehun ke badley gehun eik mudi ke badley eik mudi , jau ke badley jau eik mudi ke badley eik mudi, khajoor, khajoor ke badley eik mudi ke badley eik mudi, namak ke badley namak eik mudi ke badley eik mudi (bechaa jaey) jo ziyada dey ya ziyada ley usney sood ka maamla kiya. soney ko chaandi ke badley bechnaa jabke chaandi ziyada ho to koi harj nahin jabkey haathon haath (naqad) ho, lekin udhaar nahin. gehun ko jau ke badley bechnaa jabkey jau ziyada hon koi harj nahin jabkey haathon haath ho, lekin udhaar jayez nahin. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is hadees ko Saeed bin Abi Aruba aur Hisham Dustwaai ne ba-waaste Qatada, Muslim bin Yasar se iski sanad se riwayat kiya hai."
3350,"Abu-Ash'ash San'aani ne ye hadees ba-waaste Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kisi qadr kami beshi se riwayat ki hai aur izafa ye kiya : ''jab ye qismen mukhtalif hon to jaisey chaho becho jabkey maamla haathon haath ho.''"
3351,"Hazrat Fazaala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke khaibar ke saal Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik haar laya gaya jis mein sona aur nageeney they. Abu-Bakar aur ibne munee ne kaha : soney se latkey huey nageeney they, to eik aadmi ne usey nau ya saat Dinar mein kharid liya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin (ye kharid aur farokht durust nahin) yahan tak ke to in nageenon aur soney ko juda juda kar ley.'' us aadmi ne kaha : maine sirf qeemti patthar leney chahey hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, jab tak to inko juda juda na kar ley.'' chunanche usney isey wapis kar diya yahan tak ke unhen juda-juda kiya gaya. Ibne Esa ke lafz they  (أردت التجارة) ''maine tijarat ka irada kiya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke unki asal kitab mein lafz (حجارة) hi tha magar usey (tijarat) se badal diya."
3352,"Hazrat Fazaala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke khaibar ke din maine baara Dinar main eik haar kharida , us mein sona aur nageeney they. isliye maine unhen juda juda kiya to mujhey is mein baara Dinar se ziyada ka sona mila, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye bataya to aapney farmaya : ''juda kiye baghair na bechaa jaey.''"
3353,"Hazrat Fazaala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke khaibar waley din ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they aur yahudiyon se eik auqiya sona (masaawi (barabar) chaalis dirham) eik Dinar mein khareedtey they. Quteba ke alawa doosron ne kaha : do ya teen Dinar mein khareedtey they, phir doosrey raawi hadees ke agley alfaz bayan kerney mein muttafiq hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''soney ko soney se mat becho siwaye iskey ke wazan barabar barabar ho.''"
3354,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke main Baqee mein oont bechaa karta tha, to aisey hota ke dinaaron mein sauda karta aur dirham wasul karta ya dirahmon mein sauda karta aur Dinar wasul karta , unhen eik doosrey ke badley mein ley liya karta ya dey diya karta tha. phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya us waqt aap Ummul-momenin Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein they, maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! zara thahriye mujhey aap se eik sawal karna hai, main Baqee mein oont bechtaa hun to dinaaron se sauda karkey dirham wasul kar leta hun ya dirahmon se sauda karkey Dinar ley leta hun. unhen eik doosrey ke badley leta bhi hun aur deta bhi hun, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' koi harj nahin agar tum isi din ke bhaaw se lo aur tumharey juda honey par tum mein koi chiz baqi na ho.'' (hisab us waqt bilkul be baaq ho jaey.)"
3355,Janab Simaak ne apni sanad se aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya. pehla siyaaq ziyada kamil hai aur is mein ''us din ke bhaaw '' ka zikr nahin hai.
3356,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai ke janwar ko janwar ke badley udhaar bechaa jaey."
3357,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen hukm diya ke lashkar ki tayyari keren magar oont khatam ho gaey, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko hukm diya ke sadqe ki oontniyaan aaney tak udhaar ley lein. chunanche wo sadqe ke aaney tak do-do oonton ke badley eik-eik oont hasil kar liya kartey they."
3358,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do ghulamon ke badley eik ghulam kharida farmaya.
3359,"Janab Zaid Abu Ayash ne Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kiya ke safed gehun ko sult (jau ki eik qism) ke badley bechnaa kaisa hai? Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha : un mein se afzal kon sa hai? unhoney kaha ke safed gehun . to unhoney is se mana kar diya aur farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap se puchha gaya ke khushk khajoor ko taza khajoor ke badley bechnaa kaisa hai? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya bhala taza khajoor khushk honey par kam ho jati hai? '' Sahaba ne kaha : haan. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se mana farma diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees ko Ismail bin Umayya ne Malik ki manind riwayat kiya."
3360,Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne taza khajoor ko khushk khajoor ke badley udhaar bechney se mana farmaya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is riwayat ko Imran bin Abu-Anas ne bano makhzoom ke eik maula ke wastey se Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uski manind riwayat kiya hai.
3361,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne darkht par lagey khajoor ke phal ko) khushk ( khajoor ke badley bechney se mana farmaya hai jabkey khushk ki miqdaar maloom ho. aur usi tarah angooron ko kishmish ke badley bechnaa jabkey kishmish ki miqdaar maloom ho, aur kheti ki bikri khushk gehun ke badley jabkey uski miqdaar maloom ho. (mamnoo hai.)"
3362,"Janab Khaarija bin Zaid bin Sabit (Rahimahullah) apney walid ( Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne araayaa ki rukhsat (chhoot) inayat farmaee , yani insan khushk khajoor ka taza se tabaadla kar ley."
3363,Hazrat Sehal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne taza khajoor ki khushk khajoor ke sath bikri se mana farmaya hai. lekin araayaa ki rukhsat di hai ke insan taza khajoor ka andaza karkey (khushk ke badley kharid ley) taake wo log taza khajoor kha saken .
3364,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne riwayat kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne araayaa ki bikri mein paanch wasq se kam ya paanch wasq ki ijazat di hai. ye shak Dawud bin Husain ko hua hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees mein chaar wasq tak ka bayan aaya hai.
3365,Janab Abde-Rabba bin Saeed Ansari ne bayan kiya ke ''araayaa'' ye hai ke insan kisi ko khajoor ka koi darkht dey dey ya baagh farokht karey to us mein se eik do darkht mustashnaa kar ley taake taza phal kha sakey lekin phir usey khushk khajoor kar badley bech dey .
3366,"Ibne Is-haq ne bayan kiya ke ''araayaa'' ye hai ke koi shakhs kisi ko khajuron ke darkht hiba karey, magar baad iske un logon ka aana jana usey shaaq guzrey to unke phal ka andaza karkey khushk khajoor ke badley kharid ley ."
3367,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya hai ke phalon ko unki salahiyat zahir honey se pehley farokht kar diya jaey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farokht kerney waley aur kharidney waley dono ko mana kiya hai.
3368,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is baat se mana kiya hai ke khajuron ka zard ya surkh honey se pehley farokht kar diya jaey, ya ghalley ko jabkey wo baaliyon mein ho yahan tak ke safed ho jaeyn aur aafat zadgi se mehfooz ho jaeyn. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisey maamley se farokht kerney waley aur kharidar dono ko mana farmaya hai."
3369,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai ke ghaneematon ko taqseem se pehley hi farokht kar diya jaey ya khajuron ko farokht kiya jaey yahan tak ke tamam awaariz (nuksan) se mehfooz ho jaeyn aur is se bhi mana kiya hai ke insan kamar band (peti) ke baghair Namaz padhey."
3370,"Janab Saeed bin Meenaa (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain maine Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se suna, wo bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khajoor ko ''mushaqqah'' tak pahunchney se pehley farokht kerney se mana farmaya hai. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya ke unke ''mushaqqah'' honey se kya murad hai? to unhoney bataya ke jab khajoor surkh ya zard ho jaey aur khaney ke qabil ho jaey."
3371,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne angooron ko bechney se mana farmaya hai yahan tak ke siyah ho jaeyn aur kheti ko bechney se roka hai yahan tak ke daney sakht ho jaeyn.
3372,"Yunus kehtey hain maine Janab Abu Zinad se puchha ke phalon ko unki salahiyat zahir honey se pehley farokht karna kaisa hai aur is baarey mein kya aaya hai? to unhoney kaha : Janab Urwa bin Zuber ba-waaste Sehal bin Abi Hasma , Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya kartey they ke log phalon ko unki salahiyat numaya honey se pehley farokht kar diya kartey they. phir jab logon ke pakkey phal chunney ka waqt aata aur unke taqaza kerney waley aatey to kharidar kehtey ke phal ko sadaao , jhadaaw aur aafat lag gaee hai aur is tarah wo saudey mein heel aur hujjat kartey , jab un logon ke muqaddamaat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas bahut ziyada aaney lagey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen bator mashwara farmaya : ''agar tum in jhagdon se baaz nahin aatey ho to apney phal unki salahiyat zahir honey se pehley bechaa hi na karo.''"
3373,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne phal ki salahiyat zahir honey se pehley farokht kerney se mana farmaya hai. aur ye ke usey dirham aur Dinar (naqad qeemat) hi se farokht kiya jaey. siwaey iske ke araayaa ki soorat ho.
3374,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mutaaddid bahut salon ke liye darakhton ke phal bech deney se mana farmaya hai aur aafaat se nuqsan ki talafi (bharpaai) karaai . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se tihai tak talafi ke baarey mein koi riwayat durust nahin, ye ehale-Madina ki raey hai."
3375,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne '' bie muaawma'' (saalaha saal ke liye sauda) se mana farmaya hai jabkey (abu-Zubair aur Saeed bin Meena mein se kisi) eik ne ''bie sineen'' ka lafz bayan kya.
3376,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dhokey wale saude se mana farmaya hai. Usman ne mazeed kaha : (Hasaat saude) se bhi) mana farmaya .)
3377,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do tarah ki kharida aur farokht aur do tarah se kapda odhney se mana farmaya hai. kharida aur farokht mein mulaamisa aur munaabiza aur kapda odhney main eik (اشتمال الصماء) hai aur doosra ye ke insan apney ooper kapda is tarah se lapet kar baithey ke sharmgaah ko nanga rakhey ya us par kuchh na ho. (tafsil aagey aa rahi hai.)
3378,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees riwayat ki aur mazeed kaha : (اشتمال الصماء) ye hai ke insan eik kapdey mein uis tarah se lipat jaey ke kapdey ke dono kinaron ko baeyn kandhey par dal ley aur apni daain janib ko khula rakhey . aur bai-munaabiza ye hai ke yun kahey : jab main teri taraf ye kapda phenk dun to bai (bikri) lazim ho gaee . aur bai-mulaamisa ye hai ke chiz ko sirf apna haath laga dey , usey khol kar ya ulat palat kar na dekh sakey aur jab usey haath laga diya to bai lazim ho gaee."
3379,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai. aagey Sufiyan aur Abdur-Razzaaq ki hadisen (3377, 3378) ke ham-maani bayan ki."
3380,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamila janwar ke bachchey ke bachchey ki bai (bikri) se mana farmaya hai.
3381,"Janab Naafe ne b-waaste Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se isi hadees ki manind riwayat kya aur kaha (حبل الحبلہ) ye hai ke ye oontni bachcha janey-gi , phir jab wo paida honey wali oontni hamila hogi (to us waqt adaegi hogi)."
3382,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne khutba detey huey farmaya : logon par aisa waqt aaeyga jo kaat khaney wala hoga , sahibe-wusat (sahibe-maal) apney maal ko apney daanton se pakdey hoga (ke sadqa kerega na qarza dega balke bakheel bana rahega) halanke usey is baat ka hukm nahin. Allah taala ne farmaya hai : ''aapas mein ehsan kerney ko mat bhulo.'' aur majboor log ( majboori ki wajeh sey) sauda karengey halanke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne majboori ke saude se mana farmaya hai aur dhokey ke saudey aur phalon ke tayyar ho janey se pehley unhen farokht kar deney se mana farmaya hai."
3383,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne marfooan bayan kya : ''Allah taala farmata hai main do sharikon (saajhi daaron) ka teesra hun jab tak un mein se koi eik doosrey ki khayanat na karey. jab koi khayanat karta hai to main unke darmiyan se nikal jata hun.''
3384,Hazrat Urwa bin al-Jaad Baarqi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey eik dinar diya ke us se qurbani ka janwer ya bakri kharid laye. usney do bakriyan kharid lein aur phir eik ko eik Dinar mein bech diya. phir wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik bakri bhi ley aaya aur eik Dinar bhi. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko tijarat mein barkat ki dua di. chunanche uska haal aisa ho gaya ke wo mitti bhi kharidta to usey us mein nafa hota.
3385,Abu-Labeed kehtey hain ke Urwa baarqi (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey ye hadees bayan ki aur uskey lafz mukhtalif hain.
3386,"Hazrat Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey eik Dinar de-kar bheja ke unke liye qurbani kharida laye. chunanche usney eik Dinar mein janwar kharida aur phir usey do Dinar mein farokht kar diya, aur phir laut'tey huey eik Dinar mein doosra janwar kharida . chunanche usney (janwer ke sath) wo Dinar bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kar diya. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey sadqa kar diya aur uskey liye tijarat mein barkat ki dua farmaee."
3387,"Janab Salim bin Abdullah apney walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se riwayat kartey hain, wo kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''tum mein se jo koi chaawalon ke topey waley ki manind bin sakta ho to bin jaey.'' Sahaba ne puchha ke aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye chaawalon ke topey wala kon hai? to aapney ghaar walon ki hadees bayan ki jabke un par eik chattan aa padi thi. to un mein se her eik ne kaha tha ke apna behtareen amal bayan karo . chunanche teesrey aadmi ne kaha : ''aey Allah ! to ba-khoobi janta hai ke main eik mazdoor laya aur uskey sath chaawalon ka eik topa mazduri tey ki . jab shaam hui to maine usey uska haq pesh kiya, magar usney leney se inkar kar diya. to phir maine unhen kaasht kar diya yahan tak ke uskey liye gayen aur charwahey ikhattey kar liye . phir wo mujhey mila aur kehney laga ke mera haq mujhey dey do. to maine kaha : jao ye gayen aur unke charwahey ley jao . chunanche wo unhen haank ley gaya.''"
3388,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Badr ki jang waley din main, Hazrat Ammar aur Saad (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne aapas mein tey kiya ke jo bhi hamein milega ham teeno us mein shareek hongey . chunanche Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) to do qaidi ley aaye magar main aur Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) kuchh na la sakey."
3389,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke ham muzaar'at (yani zameen bataai par denay) mein koi harj na samajhtey they yahan tak ke maine Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is se mana farmaya hai. (Amr bin Dinar kehtey hain ke) maine ye hadees Taaus se zikr ki to unhoney kaha : mujh se Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is se mana nahin kiya balke farmaya tha : ''tum apni zameen kisi ko Atiya dey do to ye mahsool leney se behtar hai.''"
3390,Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah taala Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ki maghfirat farmaai . Allah ki qasam ! main is hadees ko un se behtar taur par janta hun. haqeeqat ye hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas do shakhs (Musaddad kehtey hain do Ansari) hazir huey us (fiqrey) ke baad dono (ki riwaayatein) muttafiq hain. dono marney maarney par tuley huey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tumhara yehi haal hai to apney khet kiraaey par mat diya karo.'' Musaddad ne mazeed kaha : Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ne itni si baat sun li : ''apney khet kiraaey par mat diya karo.''
3391,Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke ham apni zameenein kiraaey (bataai) par diya kartey they aur sath hi ye tey hota tha ke jo kuchh naaliyon par paida hoga ya jis hissey ko khud se pani pahunchta ho (to wo Malik ka hoga) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein us se mana farma diya. aur hukm diya ke ham apni zameen soney ya chaandi (currency) ke badley kiraaey par den (yani mutayyan (tai-shuda) raqam par theka kar liya karen).
3392,"Janab Hanzala bin Qais Ansari kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke zameen ko soney chaandi (naqdi) ke iwaz kiraaey par dena kaisa hai? unhoney kaha : us mein koi harj nahin. darasal log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein is tarah kartey they ke jo kuchh pani ke bahao par aur naalon ke siron par hota us par aur kuchh kheti par maamla tey kartey they. to phir aisey hota ke ye zaya ho jati aur wo bachi rehti ya wo zaya ho jati aur ye bachi rehti , logon ko kiraaey par deney ki bas yehi eik soorat raaij thi. jiski wajeh se aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is maamley se daant kar rok diya. lekin wo iwaz aur badal jo maloom aur mutayyan (tai-shuda) ho to us mein koi harj nahin hai. Ibrahim ki hadees (jo ooper zikr hui ( is se ziyada kamil hai. aur Quteba ne apni sanad mein (''عن حنظلة an  رافع'') kaha hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Yahya bin Saeed ne Hanzala se iskey misl (jaisi) riwayat ki hai."
3393,Janab Hanzala bin Qais Ansari kehtey hain ke unhoney Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke zameen ko kiraaey par dena kaisa hai? to unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zameen kiraaey par deney se mana farmaya hai. maine puchha ke kya soney aur chaandi ke badley bhi mana hai? to kaha ke soney aur chaandi ke badley mein koi harj nahin.
3394,"Janab Salim (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke unkey walid Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) zameen kiraaey (bataai) par diya kartey they yahan tak ke unhen ye khabar pahunchi ke Raafe bin Khadij Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ye hadees bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) zameen kiraaey par deney se mana farmaya kartey they. to Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se mulaqat ki aur puchha ke tum zameen ko bataai par deney ke baarey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka kya farman bayan kartey ho? to Hazrat Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke maine apney do chachaon se suna jo Badr mein shareek huey they, wo ghar walon se bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zameen kiraaey (bataai) par deney se mana kiya hai. to Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qasam ! mujhey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur ke mutalliq yehi maloom hai ke us daur mein zameen bataai par di jati thi. magar phir Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko andesha hua ke kahin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is baarey mein (baad mein) koi naee baat na farma di ho jis ka unhen ilm na ho saka ho. chunanche is bina par unhoney zameen bataai par dena tarak kar di. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is riwayat ko Ayub , Ubaidullah , Kaseer bin Farqad aur Malik (Reh.) ne ba-waaste Naafe phir Raafe aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kiya hai. aur Auzaai ne ba-waaste Hafs bin Inaan Hanfi, Naafe sey, unhoney Raafe se bayan kartey huey kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna . aur aisey hi Zaid bin Abi Aneesa ne ba-waaste hukm , Naafe sey, unhoney ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se bayan kiya ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) , Raafe ke paas aaye aur puchha ke kya tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai? to unhoney kaha : haan . aur aisey hi Ikrima bin Ammar ne Abul-Najaashi sey, unhoney Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya. kaha ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna. isi ke sath Auzaai ne Abul-Najaashi se riwayat kiya, unhoney Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney apney chacha zaheer bin Raafe sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Abul-Najaashi ka naam Ata bin Suheb hai."
3395,"Janab Sulaiman bin Yasar (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein zameen bataai par diya kartey they. to unke eik chacha unke paas aaye aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein is maamley se jo hamarey liye nafa-aawar (nafa-dene wala) tha mana farma diya hai aur Allah aur uskey Rasool ki itaat hi hamarey liye nafa-aawar aur sood-mand hai. ham ne puchha : aur wo kya hai? unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''jiskey paas zameen ho to chahiye ke khud kaasht karey ya apney bhai ko kaasht ke liye dey dey , lekin tihai ya chauthai ya mutayyan (tai-shuda) ghalley par bataai par na dey.''"
3396,Ayub ne riwayat kiya hai ke Yaala bin Hakim ne mujhey likh bheja ke maine Sulaiman bin Yasar se suna hai aur Ubaidullah ki snaadon aur iski riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kiya.
3397,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ke sahibzadey apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan se hamarey paas aaye aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein eik kaam se mana farma diya hai jo hamarey liye badey nafa wala tha, magar Allah aur uskey Rasool ki itaat mein hamarey liye bahut ziyada nafa hai. aapney hamein (kisi ki) zameen kaasht kerney se mana farma diya hai siwaye iskey ke insan khud uska Malik ho ya kisi ne usko Atiya di ho."
3398,"Janab Usaid bin Zaheer bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas aaye aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumhen eik kaam se mana farmatey hain jo tumharey liye nafa aawar (nafe-wala) tha. magar Allah aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki itaat tumharey liye us se badh kar nafa-aawar hai. bila-shuba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumhen bataai par kaasht-kaari se mana farmatey hain. aur farmaya hai : ''jo koi apni zameen se mustaghni ho to chahiye ke apney bhai ko Atiya dey dey ya waisey hi chhod dey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Shoba aur Mufazzal bin Muhalhal ne isey Mansoor se aisey hi riwayat kiya hai. Shoba ne kaha ke Usaid , Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij ke bhatijey hain."
3399,"Abu-Jaafar Khatmi ka bayan hai ke merey chacha ne mujhey aur apney ghulam ko Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) ke yahan bheja aur ham ne un se kaha : hamein aap ki taraf se muzaar'at (kheti) ke baarey main eik baat pahunchi hai (wo kaisey hai?) to unhoney kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) is mein koi harj na samajhtey they yahan tak ke unhen Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) se eik hadees pahunchi to wo khud unke paas gaey to Hazrat Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bano Harisa ke yahan tashrif laye to Zaheer ki zameen mein kheti dekhi . to farmaya : ''Zaheer ki kheti kya khoob umda hai.'' logon ne kaha : ye Zaheer ki nahin hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kaha : ''kya zameen Zaheer ki nahin?'' unhoney kaha : haan , zameen to uski hai magar falan ne kaasht kar rakhi hai. to aapney farmaya : ''apni kheti ley lo aur uska kharch usey wapis kar do.'' Hazrat Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : chunanche ham ne apni kheti ley li aur uska kharch usey ada kar diya. Saeed (bin Musaiyab) ne kaha : apney bhai ko Atiya dey do ya daraahim ke badley kiraaey par dey do."
3400,"Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai, Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne muhaaqla aur mazaabna se mana farmaya hai. (tareef aagey aaeygi) aapney farmaya : ''aadmi teen tarah se hi kaasht kaari kar sakta hai, zameen aadmi ki apni milkiyat ho to usey kaasht karey ya kisi ne usey Atiya di ho to kaasht karey ya soney chaandi ke badley kiraaey par li ho.''"
3401,Usman bin Sehal bin Raafe bin Khadij ne bayan kiya ke main yateem tha aur (apney dada) Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ki sarparasti mein tha. maine unke sath hajj bhi kiya. mera bhai Imran bin Sehal unke paas aaya aur kaha ke ham ne apni zameen falan aurat ko do so dirham ke badley thekey par de-di hai. to unhoney kaha ke usey chhod do . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zameen kiraaey (thekey) par deney se mana farmaya hai.
3402,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke usney zameen kaasht kar rakhi thi ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wahan se guzrey jabkey wo usey pani dey raha tha. to aapney us se puchha : ''ye kis ne kaasht ki hai aur zameen kis ki hai.'' arz kiya ke kaasht meri hai, beej mera hai aur mehnat bhi meri hai, mujhey aadha hissey milega aur aadha bano falan ko . to aapney farmaya : ''tum dono ne sood ka maamla kiya, zameen uskey malikon ko wapis kar do aur apna kharch ley lo.''"
3403,Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney kisi ki zameen malikon ki ijazat ke baghair kaasht ki ho uskey liye us kheti mein se kuchh nahin. albatta kharcha ley sakta hai.''
3404,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne muhaaqla , mazaabna , mukhaabira aur muaawma se mana farmaya hai. eik raawi ne (muaawma ki bajaey ( ''بیع السنین'' kaha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne istasna kar leney se bhi mana farmaya hai. albatta araayaa ki rukhsat (chhoot) di hai."
3405,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne riwayat kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mazaabna , muhaaqla aur istasna kar leney se mana farmaya hai siwaey iske ke maloom aur mutayyan (tai-shuda) ho."
3406,"Janab Abu-Zubair , Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kartey hain, kehtey hain : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna hai : ''jo shakhs mukhaabira (mazaariat (kheti))  na chhodey to usey chahiye ke Allah aur uskey Rasool se jang ke liye tayyar rahey.''"
3407,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mukhaabira se mana farmaya hai. (Sabit bin Hajjaj ne puchha ke) mukhaabira se kya murad hai? unhoney kaha : ye ke to zameen ko aadhi , tihai ya chauthai par hasil kar ley."
3408,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehale-khaibar se maamla tey farmaya tha ke jo phal ya kheti aaeygi us mein se aadha unhen milega.
3409,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ki khajuren aur wahan ki zameenein ehale khaibar ko is shart par de-di thin ke wo un mein apney kharch par mehnat karengey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko unka aadha phal milega.
3410,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab khaibar Fateh kar liya aur shart ki ke musalman uski zameen aur uskey soney chaandi ke Malik hain. to khaibar walon ne kaha ke ham aap ki nisbat zameen ke ziyada mahir hain. aap ye hamein dey den aur shart ye rahi ke aadha ham aap ko dengey aur aadha khud rakhengey. chunanche aapney is shart par zameen unhen dey di. phir jab phal chunney ka mausam aaya to aapney Hazrat Abdullah bin Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) ko bheja jo khajuron ke phal ka andaza laga kar aaye aur is amal ko ehale-Madina (خرص) ''andaza lagana'' kehtey hain. Hazrat Abdullah bin Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke falan baagh mein is qadr hai aur falan mein is qadr. to unhoney kaha : aey ibne Rawaha ! to ne ham par ziyada laga diya hai. to unhoney jawab diya ke maine un phalon ka jo andaza lagaya hai, uska main zimmey-daar hun, main uska nisf (aadha) tumhen deta hun. yahudiyon ne kaha : yehi wo haq (aur insaf) hai jis se aasman aur zameen qaaim hain jo aapney kaha ham uskey leney par razi hain."
3411,Jaafar bin Burqaan ne apni mazkura sanad se is hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya aur (فحزر) ka lafz istimal kya. aur (وكل صفراء وبيضاء) ke baad yani (الذهب والفضة له) bhi kaha.
3412,Janab Muqsim ne bayan kiya ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar Fateh kar liya. aur Zaid ki (mazkura baala) hadees ki manind bayan kiya. uskey lafz they (فحزر النخل) ''phal ki miqdaar ka andaza lagaya'' aur kaha : (agar tum is andazey par mutmain nahin ho to) ''phal ki tudaai main kar lunga aur jo maine kaha hai uska aadha tumhen de-dun ga.''
3413,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke jab khajuren pakney ke qarib aatin to unke khaye janey se pehley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Abdullah bin Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) ko rawana farmatey wo unke phalon ki miqdaar ka andaza lagatey. phir wo yahudiyon ko ikhtiyar detey ke wo ya to is andaza karda miqdaar se apna hissey ley lein ya musalmanon ko dey den , aur ye sab isliye hota ke phal khaye janey se pehley uski Zakat (daswen hisse) ka hisab lagaya ja sakey aur taqseem kiya ja sakey."
3414,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke jab Shan wale Allah ne khaibar apney Rasool ko bataur fai inayat farmaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yahudiyon ko uski zameenon par wesay hi rehney diya jaisey ke wo pehley they aur unke aur apney darmiyan mutayyan hissey tey kar liye . chunanche aapney Hazrat Abdullah bin Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) ko bheja jinhon ne un par phalon ka andaza lagaya.
3415,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat ibne Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) ne chaalis hazar wasq ka andaza lagaya tha. aur phir jab yahudiyon ko ikhtiyar diya to unhoney phal ley liya aur unke zimmey (musalmanon ka ( bees hazar wasq aa gaya.
